{"tid":1067634,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜利物浦時隔三十年再度奪取英格蘭頂級聯賽冠軍","createTime":"2019-03-18T15:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T18:10:31.000Z","uid":68080,"like":46,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d4966f5cd50247e4acaee88f76e39016a9a8f1ae","tid":1067634,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"2018-19英超聯賽最終排名如下<br />\n1. 利物浦<br />\n2. 曼城<br />\n3. 熱刺<br />\n4. 阿仙奴<br />\n5. 車路士<br />\n6. 曼聯<br />\n<br />\n今季利物浦成功把握住曼城既失誤 以一分既領先優勢奪冠<br />\n<br />\n而阿仙奴保持第四之餘 仲成功奪得歐霸冠軍 復興在望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛daddy果然勁過垃圾雲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n車路士就四大皆空 賣埋夏薩特 黎緊ban兩個轉會窗 會唔會崩潰就睇今次轉會窗既運作<br />\n但係就係因為形勢咁惡劣 無名帥肯黎 被逼留用煙sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望煙sir可以帶領隊波打出sarri ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱刺星散 大家無辦法再用未來黎麻醉自己 充分認識到想要爭冠先要轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於曼聯以第六完成賽季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歐聯俾巴塞兩回合6比0恥辱性淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n士氣大失之下英超不斷失分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b62aa9fada307d992eefbd8f5d42c0a19ca423e","tid":1067634,"uid":38189,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"錯晒喎 利記冇冠軍 阿仙奴冇頭四 車路士拎歐霸 曼聯大炒巴塞"},{"pid":"4f0579d26feeb4f9b4eccadd0c8dd8e1bf515cb5","tid":1067634,"uid":56947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"我利威武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025dc3b023adbd0013f640dba5b02cc8ce2bede5","tid":1067634,"uid":9145,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"雲你老母狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6466b3b4f1079933028175662e56144a2848131","tid":1067634,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"5b62aa9fada307d992eefbd8f5d42c0a19ca423e","tid":1067634,"uid":38189,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"錯晒喎 利記冇冠軍 阿仙奴冇頭四 車路士拎歐霸 曼聯大炒巴塞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"事實完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認清現實啦 曼聯都係輸巴塞 六弟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利物浦今季無冠軍天無眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06df9ddaaec049885879a090dc264af029d62942","tid":1067634,"uid":82851,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"邊個再敢笑利冇英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52fb73a307d6af494ce1a2ca97007c90a0ded96","tid":1067634,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"025dc3b023adbd0013f640dba5b02cc8ce2bede5","tid":1067634,"uid":9145,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"雲你老母狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"跟住叫既者<br />\n而家唔叫雲狗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3018b72b807816fd2ff3b51b8f94abcb8edb87","tid":1067634,"uid":68080,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06df9ddaaec049885879a090dc264af029d62942","tid":1067634,"uid":82851,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"邊個再敢笑利冇英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"由呢個英超冠軍開始<br />\n利物浦將會稱霸英格蘭30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3ea6d7e053531ca24e10e67ce44943a4a21d52","tid":1067634,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:58:20.0